OOC: Sure it's moding but Aerosmith's not coming back in the foreseeable 
future

::Kaiser::
       He looks at Tyrael warily.  "Did you just issue an order to a 
Tripredacus general, field commander?"  He relaxes after a moment.  "Good.  
You will do well.  I am no longer interested in leading."  He shoves 
Blackheart into a CR chamber with all the grace of a maimed elephant, then 
thinking better of it pulls him back out and removes his spark for temporary 
storage.  He drags Blackheart's old body around leaving his spark on a shelf.

       He works his way down to Tyrael's location with Blackheart's body.  He 
dumps it unceremoniously at Tyrael's feet.  "Your body, sir."

--part1_b6.180356cf.2b7476f3_boundary
